{
  "stem": "7546.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since he was a doctor, he wore a band stating that he's a doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they immediately put him into work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since he didn't want to lose me, he made me his assistant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I helped him in a lot of things, as far as putting band-aids on, roll band-aids, unroll band-aids, see who is still worthwhile saving, who is not.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In most cases, I just covered the body and we walked away, because there was no way we could-- we could take the body.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And once the Germans came in to Warsaw, the fight was over, we walked back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The walking back is a long story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- actually, I remember every day, but we made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We came home and we found my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had assigned to us a cellar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On that long walk back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that long-- we did not sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not sleep, we did not sleep, we did not sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walked, and we tried to make it as fast as possible to get into Warsaw to be part of the fight against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Walking back was much easier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Walking back, we were able to hitch sometimes a ride on a horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did sleep over two or three nights, and we made it back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we came back, we found the whole family was in disarray.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In disarray.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister, naturally she thought that she lost her husband, and her son was just born while we were away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So naturally, we went over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Julek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beautiful little boy, gorgeous little boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went home, and we found out that so far, nothing has happened to our family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are together.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
